
Read these instructions before disregarding them.
To install Gray Matter:

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Extract the source:
	 Type: unzip "Gray Matter.zip"
	 Type: cd "Gray Matter"

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Edit inc/config.h (if necessary):
	 This should be self-explanatory.  If it isn't, just skip it.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Compile:
	 Type: make clean
	 Type: make

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Run:
	 Type: xboard -fcp bin/gray

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If something goes wrong, email any member of The Gray Matter Team with a
detailed description of your problem.  (Email addresses are provided in:
doc/credits)  We'll reply as quickly as we can.

Happy hacking!  :-)
The Gray Matter Team

